After cloning run 'git submodule init' , 'git submodule update' to pull frontend which is located in 'client/'

How to run:

1. install npm
2. install mongodb
3. run in project root folder 'npm install'
4. run in project root folder 'npm start'

A new db will be initialised. The default user is 'root' and the password is 'P@ssw0rd'
If you want to have the site accessible from other devices change the route in 'client/src/setupProxy.js' to contain you LAN ip addr(for lan access) or public ip(for internet access)